{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Grease a large baking dish (approx. 26 cm x 24 cm x 5 cm) then set aside.","Butter bread slices then cut in half diagonally, creating triangles. Arrange bread in overlapping layers in prepared baking dish.","Place chocolate in mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 9<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add remaining 80 g butter, sugar and cream then melt <b>2 min\/50°C\/speed 2<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then melt again <b>2 min\/50°C\/speed 2<b>.","Add eggs and cinnamon then blend <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Pour over bread in dish and leave to soak for 10 minutes. Meanwhile, preheat oven to 180°C.","Bake for 25-35 minutes (180°C), covering with foil if top begins to brown too much. Serve hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["130 g butter, plus extra for greasing","300 g sliced white bread","200 g dark chocolate, small pieces or callets","100 g golden caster sugar","420 g whipping cream","3 large eggs","¼ tsp ground cinnamon"]}],"id":"r83134","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-CmerY0AA148\/XZaosxCQNKI\/AAAAAAAAhMw\/cQzqPSRWIPsPtKG8uiKY0RhgsnWJuvkYACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_vUfvLmMRgJ1LA1BN.png","title":"Chocolate Bread and Butter Pudding","publishedAt":"2015-12-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8.2 g","fat":"50.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"47.3 g","calories":"2837 kJ \/ 678 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large baking dish (approx. 26 cm x 24 cm x 5 cm), aluminium foil, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Bread and butter pudding has long been considered, like rice pudding, a deliciously filling yet low-budget option for a dessert. This rich, chocolate-laden version is gooey and deliciously moreish. Enjoy with pouring cream or vanilla ice cream."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h","8 portions"]}